snippet.title: IMMORTALITY - Reveal Trailer for the New Sam Barlow Game
snippet.description: IMMORTALITY is an interactive film trilogy from Sam Barlow, creator of Her Story. What happened to Marissa Marcel? Explore footage from her lost movies to solve the mystery.
